HIM, 
This morning, I dropped off the laptop with a power cord and cover memo for Maxwell to use when reviewing her 
discovery. Attached please find a copy of the cover memo. 
I also dropped off a hard drive and CD containing a new discovery production for Maxwell. Attached please find the two 
cover letters. 
Last week, we sent out via FedEx a hard drive containing a separate production, which included replacements of 
numerous files that Maxwell has been unable to review from prior productions. The accompanying cover letters are 
attached. Would you please confirm that the drive has been provided to Maxwell? 
Thanks very much, as always, for your help. 
Assistant United States Attorney 
Southern District of New York 
New York, NY 10007 
EFTA00029978
